    </div>
    <div style="background: #42a5f5; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 6px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: #fff;">
      <span style="font-weight: 600;">Review 5</span><span>After 30 days</span>
    </div>
